{"tid":1404320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】今日新口號","createTime":"2019-08-04T03:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:39:58.000Z","uid":118219,"like":431,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"f4716c242ea465ee066ef384b10bb80184f53b00","tid":1404320,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"「一齊黎 一齊散 一個都不能少」<br />\n<br />\n已經有好撚多個手足比啲恐龍食咗 真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家仲要留力啊！<br />\n<br />\n知道好多前線話有晒gear已經準備比好晒 <br />\n但少你一個真係少好撚多 11月區選我地又少左百9幾張票啦<br />\n<br />\n我都發過夢 我都知當下好熱血覺得走左好無義氣 人多先好辦事 走左你一個之後啲手足會更危險<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但香港人不能再接受失去手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該前線 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">「一齊黎 一齊散 一個都不能少」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳 好人一生平安健康"},{"pid":"a137142ee5f8bed02b0421a5eb542f531681a5f1","tid":1404320,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dbf1daec4945f9d4c7285da73ff9669125d512b","tid":1404320,"uid":181581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:02:20.000Z","msg":"又西環啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c510f86363a14f04364d51fbeba98b204b71a018","tid":1404320,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8316b2d33786780baa711b6d7a71cb64d1371e5d","tid":1404320,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dbf1daec4945f9d4c7285da73ff9669125d512b","tid":1404320,"uid":181581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:02:20.000Z","msg":"又西環啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"今日同兩老係屋企樓下遊行 冇得去西環"},{"pid":"9915e57f567b6a8b9c147c8775a57910c17afbc6","tid":1404320,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,